{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "第五回「又是圆月」。丁鹏与青青趁众人醉酒之际准备离开狐谷，黑袍老人突然现身阻拦。丁鹏为保护青青不惜以命相搏，黑袍老人被其真情打动，揭示自己实为青青的祖父，此番考验只为验证丁鹏对青青的真心。二人通过考验回到人间。青青叮嘱丁鹏复仇须谨慎：不到万不得已不出手，出刀则必取性命，凡事留一线。场景转至万松山庄，柳若松夫妇得知丁鹏未死且豪阔异常，惊惧之余密谋派杀手宋中前往杭州刺杀丁鹏。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我知道你心里在想什么，我也知道你一定不舍得离开这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我的确有点舍不得离开这地方，可是我更舍不得离开你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你是不是真的愿意带我走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "当然是真的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "如果你改变了主意，现在还来得及，我可以让你一个人走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我说过，我到哪里去，你就到哪里去，有我就有你！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你不后悔？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我为什么要后悔？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "如果我们要走，最好还是快走，免得他们醒来……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "他们绝不会醒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "这酒是用我爷爷的秘方酿成的，就算神仙喝下去，也得要过六个时辰之后才会醒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "如果有六个时辰就够了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，六个时辰已经足够了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "你笑什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍老人",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "这八条小狐狸都有两手，这条母狐狸更不是省油的灯，我要一个个把他们全都摆平，还不太容易，想不到居然有人先替我把他们摆平了，倒省了我不少事。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "你是谁？想来干什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍老人",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我要来剥你们的狐皮，替我的孙子做件外衣。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍老人",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "就凭你这小狐狸的这点道行，还差得远。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍老人",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "你是不是想去找那老狐狸来？你难道忘了，七月十五，月圆子正，阴阳交泰，正是他练功最吃紧的时候，就算我当着他面前剥你的皮，他也不敢动的，否则只要一走火人魔，就万劫不复了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍老人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你是人，不是狐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍老人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我只杀狐，不杀人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍老人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你走吧，最好快走，莫等我改变了主意。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍老人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你为什么还不走？你是不是也想陪他们一起死？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "如果你要杀她，就得先杀了我。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你真的愿意跟我死在一起？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我说过，有我就有你，不管你到哪里去，我都陪着你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍老人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你真的要陪她死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "真的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍老人",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你要死还不容易！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "只怕也不太容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我真的没有死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我还活着，你怎么会死？你若死了，我怎么会还活着？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "只要我们在一起，我们就不会死，我们生生世世都会在一起。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "可是我想不通！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "什么事你想不通？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我想不通那个穿着黑袍的老怪物怎么会放过我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "因为那个老怪物，并不是个真的老怪物。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "他就是我的爷爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我爷爷知道你迟早一定是会想走的，我们的一举一动他都知道，所以，他和我奶奶打了个赌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "他们赌什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "如果你真的对我好，如果你还肯为我死，他就让我们走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "现在他们才相信，你并没有骗我，不管你到哪里去，都不会抛下我，所以他们才让我跟你走！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "这里是什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "这里是人间。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我们真的已回到人间来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "真的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我一定要先去看看我的娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你能不能带我去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我一定要带你去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我说过，不管我到哪里去，都一定带着你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我当然要去见你的母亲，可是我不想再见别的人了，以后不管你要去跟什么人相见，我最好都不要露面。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你应该知道是为了什么。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "可是别人绝不会看出你……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我知道别人绝不会看出我是狐，可是……不管怎么样，我总是狐，能够不和凡人见面，还是不要见面的好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "只要是你不愿做的事，我绝不会勉强你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "但是有时候我却一定要勉强你，而且一定要你听我的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "去见过你母亲后，你准备做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我知道你要去做什么，你不但要出人头地，还要出气！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我们临走的时候，我爷爷再三关照我，如果你想成名，想复仇，有几件事你一定要牢牢记住。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "什么事？你说！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "不到万不得已时，你千万不能出手，对方如果是个不值得你出手的人，你也千万不能够出手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你第一次出手，一定要谨慎选择一个很好的对象，你只要能击败他，就可以名动江湖，那么你就不必再去跟别人结仇！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "因为我爷爷说，不管你的武功多高，名气多大，如果你的仇家太多，迟早总有一天还是会被人逼上绝路。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我明白他老人家的意思，我一定会照他的话做。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "所以你出手不能太无情，更不能赶尽杀绝！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "如果你要别人真心尊敬你，就一定要替别人留下一条路走！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我懂！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "还有一件事更重要！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "这是我奶奶给你的，所以我爷爷还是让你带了出来，可是你不到万不得巳时，绝不能用这把刀！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "如果你要用这把刀，就一定要让对方死在这把刀下，只要刀一出鞘，就绝不能留下对方的活口。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "如果对方不是我一定要杀的人，如果对方还没有把我逼上绝路，我就不能用这把刀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你绝不能用！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "但是你可以放心，以你现在的武功，无论你用什么刀都已必将无敌于天下！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "难道我上次替你从关东带回来的虎鞭也没有用？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "你是不是已经查出了那位公子的来历？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "他是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "他是我们的一个熟人，可是你绝对猜不出他是谁的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "他叫丁鹏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "丁鹏？就是那个丁鹏？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "就是他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "想不到他居然还没有死，你是不是很高兴？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "我高兴什么？他最恨的并不是你，是我。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "他既然还没有死，迟早总会来找我们的，但是我实在想不到，一个像他那样的穷小子，怎么会忽然变得如此豪阔？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "大难不死必有后福，那次他居然能逃走，我们居然找不到，就表示这小子有造化，有造化的人，就算走在路上，也会捡着大元宝。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "他既然要来找我们算账，为什么不爽爽快快地找上门来，为什么要在我们对面去盖那样一座大宅院，他究竟在打什么主意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "人心隔肚皮，一个活人心里在打什么主意，别人永远猜不透的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "如果这个活人忽然死了呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "一个人如果死了，就什么主意都没有了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "只可惜他不会死的，他既然能活到现在，要他死就不大容易。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "虽然不太容易，也不太难。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "从那次事到现在才四年，一个人如果运气特别好，在四年之中，可能会发横财。武功就不一样了，武功是要一天天用苦功练成的，绝不会像大元宝一样，绝不会从天上掉下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "他不敢上门来找我们，就因为他虽然发了财，武功却还是跟以前差不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "以他的武功，就算遇到名师，就算再苦练十年，也绝不是小宋的对手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "小宋？你说的是宋中。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "姓宋名中，一剑送终，除了他还有谁？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "这个人我倒认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "我知道你认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你好像也认得的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "我认得没有用，你认得才有用。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "因为他只听你的话，你要他往东，他绝不敢往西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你的意思是说，我要他杀人，他也会去。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "你要他杀一个人，他绝不敢杀两个，你要他去杀张三，他绝不敢去杀李四。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "如果我要他去杀丁鹏，丁鹏就什么主意都没有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "一点也不错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 686,
      "line_end": 686
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "只可惜这两年他太出风头了，已经变得又骄又狂，怎么会听我这么样一个老太婆的话？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "这两年我出的风头也不小，连我都要听你这老太婆的话，他怎么不敢不听？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 694
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "他真的听话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 698
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "现在你总该知道我是不是真的听话了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 724,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "听话的人，总有好处的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 728,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你想不想知道那位丁鹏丁公子这两天在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 730
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 732
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "这两天他正在游西湖，就住在贾似道以前住的半边堂，红梅阁里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "这位丁公子的气派倒真不小。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 738
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "你当然也不会不知道小宋这两天在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 742
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你想见他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "很想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你为什么不早说，如果我早知道你想见他，就把他带来了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 748,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "现在呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 752
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "现在要找他只怕已很不容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 754,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 756
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "因为我已经叫他到一个很远很远的地方去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 758,
      "line_end": 758
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "这个很远很远的地方，究竟是什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 760,
      "line_end": 760
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "杭州，西湖，红梅阁，半边堂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "我虽然是个活人，可是我心里会打什么主意，用不着等我说出来，你也能猜得到的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 766
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "柳夫人",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你真的是个活人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_liu_fu_ren",
      "text": "我已经死了，就算还没有完全死，最多也只剩下了半条命。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 774,
      "line_end": 776
    }
